@startuml
start

:Open Job Form;
note right
User opens the job application form.
end note

:Enter Job Details;
note right
User enters company, position, and application date.
end note

:Submit Application;
note right
User submits the completed job form.
end note

:Validate Data;
note right
System validates the entered job information.
end note

:Save Job Application;
note right
System stores the job application.
end note

:Show Confirmation;
note right
System displays confirmation to the user.
end note

stop
@enduml